(61556, 'Renato Medina', 'For fun....:-D\n\nTheory is when you know something, but it doesn’t work. Practice is when something works, but you don’t know why. Programmers combine theory and practice: Nothing works and they don’t know why.', '14811750159_10152698604420160', '2013-03-14 21:23:15'),
