(62737, 'Bruno Batista', 'Alguem ja ouviu falar sobre Blade Engine? ou HAML?\n\nSão templates engines:\n\nPHP Puro:\n<?php echo $this->item; ?>\n\nBlade:\n{{ $this->item }}\n\nPHP Puro:\n<?php foreach ($this->items as $item) : ?>\nDo something\n<?php endforeach; ?>\n\nBlade:\n@foreach ($this->items as $item)\nDo something\n@endforeach', '14811750159_10152074393180160', '2012-08-22 19:31:12'),
